19/*
20 * attribute mask
21*/
22#define ATTR_MASK_READABLE (0x00) // readable
23#define ATTR_MASK_WRITABLE (0x01) // writable
24#define ATTR_MASK_TOKENIZE (0x02) // saved to a native sdk token
25#define ATTR_NOT_USE (0x04) //
26#define ATTR_MASK_MANUFACTURER_SPECIFIC (0x80) // manufacturer specific
27#define ATTR_MASK_RESERVED (0x10) // reserved
28#define ATTR_MASK_SINGLETON (0x20) // attribute is singleton
29#define ATTR_MASK_CLIENT (0x40) // client attribute
30#define ATTR_MASK_TOKEN_FAST (0x80) // saved to a tuya token
